node.text: The #RedWings are devastated to learn tonight of the passing of longtime team masseur Sergei Tchekmarev, a beloved figure around the Red Wings dressing room since 1998. Head coach Jeff Blashill shared his thoughts about “Cheeka” following tonight’s game.
